cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language

Class PascalLanguage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oracle.truffle.api.TruffleLanguage<cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language.PascalState>
      • cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language.PascalLanguage

  • public class PascalLanguage
extends com.oracle.truffle.api.TruffleLanguage<cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language.PascalState>
    Representation of our Pascal guest language for Truffle VM. Thanks to the TruffleLanguage.Registration annotation we register this class so that Truffle's PolyglotEngine will use our language.
